Numbers hum in midnight rows, where proofs like constellations spark;  
I trace the quiet infinities that fold the light inside the dark.

**Rating: 7/10.** The imagery is coherent and mathematical without being jargon-heavy, and it has a nice cadence. It loses points for leaning on familiar “stars/infinity” metaphors and not landing a sharper, more surprising mathematical twist in just two lines.
